{"tid":1701100,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"你地校長快撚啲表態得唔得？","createTime":"2019-11-09T00:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T20:13:18.000Z","uid":147470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74ed3de5ee216b087870f5e73d87f0a513975e76","tid":1701100,"uid":147470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:15:36.000Z","msg":"中大同科大有幫手譴責同追究<br />\n但都係學生出事之後先幫拖<br />\n<br />\n中大就學生爆肚講晒啲經歷先醒覺<br />\n科大就學生重傷先開始轉幫學生<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">結論係: 其他大學校長唔該快啲幫手出聲<br />\n               嚴查警暴，保護學生</span><br />\n<br />\n唔係次次都出事燒到埋黎先出聲<br />\n大學校長一日唔幫口比壓力Popo<br />\n一日學生都係受盡各方壓力底下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">義士們，我們替你們走下去！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c624201993ac8dda8916e8d13621673e2e91660d","tid":1701100,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b594ca0c82163aed1d0519097bf518cff874b165","tid":1701100,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:49:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">入去rt + like + reply</span><br />\n（突發）Senator Hawley 同 Solomon Yue 知道議員被拉！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700966\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700966</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n仲有Senator Rubio都知道周同學死訊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/marcorubio/status/1192876824868671488?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmarcorubio%2Fstatus%2F1192876824868671488%3Fs%3D21&d=tP4MK%2BV56WczluUfImobOBnxOJLX742lx1SCoot1iYY%3D&h=f0faf2b3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/fra